      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$King Cassius$<BR>Hmm?! Who is the "girl" they are talking about here?<BR>Hmm... Could it be the female knight 'Aisha'?<BR>Why was this thing still at Memoria...?<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cassius studies the records carefully)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
